  "wikitext": "\n'''7-4-225\n\nAlternative term: Angle of shearing resistance\n\nThe limiting value of the angle between the reaction on a plane within a soil mass at which shearing may occur and the normal to that plane.\n\n\nNote: The tangent of the angle of internal friction is the coefficient of friction for the soil.\n\n{{IALAFooter}}\n\n{{languages|Angle of internal friction}}\n[[Category:7.4 Environmental Data]]\n[[Category:Alphabetical Index]]\n[[Category:IALA Dictionary 1970-89 Edition]]\n[[Category:IALA Dictionary 2023 Revision]]"
